    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  BasicGeometricShape
    This abstract class is a basic implementation of a geometric shape.
    class  Circle
    This class describes an ellipse defined by it's position, diameter and color given as an object of java.awt.Color.
    class  Ellipse
    This class describes an ellipse defined by it's position, height, width and color given as an object of java.awt.Color.
    class  Line
    This class describes a line defined by it's position, height, width, angle and color given as an object of java.awt.Color.
    class  Point
    This class describes a point defined by it's position, and color given as an object of java.awt.Color.
    class  Rectangle
    This class describes a rectangle defined by it's position, height, width and color given as an object of java.awt.Color.
    class  Square
    This class describes a square defined by it's position, side and color given as an object of java.awt.Color.
